#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/hosts_instructors/workshop_needs.md:1
msgid "Workshop needs"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/hosts_instructors/workshop_needs.md:3
msgid ""
"Participants are expected to come with their own laptops.  Setting up a "
"computer lab space is not necessary. Before the workshop, participants will "
"receive instructions on what software they need to install and set up on "
"their laptops."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/hosts_instructors/workshop_needs.md:5
msgid "Venue"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/hosts_instructors/workshop_needs.md:7
msgid ""
"A good venue is crucial to establishing a positive learning environment.  "
"Some things to consider include:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/hosts_instructors/workshop_needs.md:9
msgid ""
"Tables arranged so participants can watch the instructor, use their laptops,"
" and talk with their peers.  Fold up desks are usually not a good choice."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/hosts_instructors/workshop_needs.md:10
msgid ""
"Tables should also be arranged so helpers and instructors can easily mingle "
"around the room."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/hosts_instructors/workshop_needs.md:11
msgid ""
"The room should have a projector and screen that everyone can see, with "
"HDMI, VGA, and Mac adapters to allow anyone to plug in their laptop."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/hosts_instructors/workshop_needs.md:12
msgid ""
"High speed Wi-Fi internet access that can withstand everyone using it "
"together. This may include securing guest access codes."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/hosts_instructors/workshop_needs.md:13
msgid ""
"Power outlets for all participants. This may include setting up extension "
"cords or power strips."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/hosts_instructors/workshop_needs.md:14
msgid ""
"High table or podium that instructor can stand at while teaching.  A flat "
"podium is important; it's difficult to use a laptop on a slanted podium."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/hosts_instructors/workshop_needs.md:15
msgid ""
"Refreshments. People learn better when they are well fed.  They also won't "
"lose as much instructional time if they don't have to leave to get coffee."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/hosts_instructors/workshop_needs.md:17
msgid "Equipment and materials"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/hosts_instructors/workshop_needs.md:19
msgid ""
"Power strips, as noted above, to ensure everyone's laptop stays charged"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/hosts_instructors/workshop_needs.md:20
msgid ""
"Sticky notes in two contrasting colors. These are an important part of how "
"we get feedback during a lesson.  We should have enough for each person to "
"have about 8 of each color."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/hosts_instructors/workshop_needs.md:21
msgid "Name tags to help people get to know each other."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/hosts_instructors/workshop_needs.md:22
msgid "Extra pens and paper in case people want to take notes by hand"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/hosts_instructors/workshop_needs.md:23
msgid "Sign in sheets"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/hosts_instructors/workshop_needs.md:24
msgid ""
"Flipchart or whiteboard with felt-tip pen (ideally several in different "
"colors) for the instructor to visualise concepts or note important details."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/hosts_instructors/workshop_needs.md:26
msgid "Accessibility"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/hosts_instructors/workshop_needs.md:28
msgid ""
"It's important to make sure the workshop space is accessbile to all "
"individuals. The registration form should ask whether instructors, helpers, "
"and learners need any advance arrangements to ensure they can participate in"
" the event. This may include considering whether or not:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/hosts_instructors/workshop_needs.md:30
msgid ""
"Building and room are accessible to those who can not use stairs (ramps, "
"elevators, etc.)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/hosts_instructors/workshop_needs.md:31
msgid "Restrooms are accessible"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/hosts_instructors/workshop_needs.md:32
msgid "There is a microphone for instructors"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/hosts_instructors/workshop_needs.md:33
msgid "The screen is large enough and bright enough to be easily read"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/hosts_instructors/workshop_needs.md:34
msgid "The building and room can accommodate service animals"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/hosts_instructors/workshop_needs.md:35
msgid "Lactation space is provided"
msgstr ""
